{
  "stem": "12666.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the Nuremberg proceedings are available.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were printed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we did have to review.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they asked me to fill in as a reviewer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was working as a reviewer through the different trials.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did have a lot of journalists in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were sitting-- they were living in the palace of Faber, you know, the one that makes pencils?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the headquarters of the press there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was invited down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was interesting to meet press from all different countries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did even have-- I remember meeting a Bulgarian newspaperman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And another thing, we did discuss the crime committed in the Katyn Forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You probably have heard about that crime, where officers were executed by the Soviet secret police.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a Bulgarian doctor as a witness at the Nuremberg trial saying that he did visit the Katyn forest.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the strange thing that he said-- he said that the Polish officers that were killed there, some of them had summer uniforms.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The others had winter uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know what that means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, that was not picked up by, by the press or by anybody else.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you see, during the summer, it was the advance of the German-- I mean, the Germans were advancing, but it was still under Soviet control.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In winter, it was already under German control.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So some people theorized that the Germans didn't find enough corpses there, so they added some new ones.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know whether this is true or not, but that, that was interesting that the Katyn Forest came up during the Nuremberg trial.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It did, did come up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many other trials we, we, we did discuss, too, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you stay in Nuremberg well after the end of the trial?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
